{"tid":1611443,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"<和理非> Report Hotel Indigo Hong Kong Island","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:31:37.000Z","uid":321724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"688154f64f0016bf10ad62b202f0ff561e51f093","tid":1611443,"uid":321724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"我係P牌仔<br />\n<br />\n琴晚indigo<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放狗入屋</span>個單野其實好嚴重<br />\n<br />\n酒店業最重要既係保障顧客既安全<br />\n可以不歡迎某啲人進入私人範圍<br />\n但你歡迎佢，即使借廁所佢都係客<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家可以係所有online platform<br />\n甚至寫email去IHG度投訴呢間不知所謂既酒店<br />\n例如係tripadvisor, <a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=6a41da41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">booking.com</a>, expedia<br />\n希望佢可以快撚啲執笠<br />\n<br />\n同時警告其他行家唔好有樣學樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444c46d15720996dcafa2b85fe5d4a66c26b5f00","tid":1611443,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:31:37.000Z","msg":"銀髮軍師 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非</span>加入 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戰況大增千倍</span>的新戰術<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613583</a>"}]}